1
00:00:45,254 --> 00:00:48,966
PERFECT CROWN

2
00:00:59,851 --> 00:01:00,978
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

3
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:02,980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

4
00:01:03,939 --> 00:01:04,940
Tell me.

5
00:01:05,566 --> 00:01:07,234
Who are you trying to save here? Yourself?

6
00:01:07,317 --> 00:01:08,402
Or the Grand Prince?

7
00:01:11,154 --> 00:01:12,155
Him.

8
00:01:14,199 --> 00:01:16,076
I can save myself.

9
00:01:17,369 --> 00:01:18,370
You…

10
00:01:19,371 --> 00:01:20,664
Please, Father.

11
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:34,052
Divorce him.

12
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:39,433
You bear the brunt of the allegations,
from ambitions for the throne

13
00:01:39,516 --> 00:01:41,560
to the staged marriage,

14
00:01:42,185 --> 00:01:43,353
and divorce him.

15
00:01:45,731 --> 00:01:46,732
Father…

16
00:01:46,815 --> 00:01:48,650
When he loses you, his weakness,

17
00:01:48,734 --> 00:01:50,902
the opposition will
have nothing left to target.

18
00:01:50,986 --> 00:01:51,987
Then the Grand Prince

19
00:01:53,071 --> 00:01:55,449
will be able to fight back
without restraint.

20
00:02:09,046 --> 00:02:10,047
What if…

21
00:02:13,008 --> 00:02:14,885
What if I want to save myself?

22
00:02:15,385 --> 00:02:17,012
You said to choose between us.

23
00:02:19,056 --> 00:02:20,182
That path, too,

24
00:02:21,308 --> 00:02:22,309
leads to divorce.

25
00:02:27,981 --> 00:02:29,941
Get out of that hellhole.

26
00:02:31,234 --> 00:02:32,694
Avoid getting hurt any further.

27
00:03:03,684 --> 00:03:07,604
PERFECT CROWN

28
00:03:08,146 --> 00:03:09,815
EPISODE 10

29
00:03:14,444 --> 00:03:16,905
His Royal Highness is inside.

30
00:03:41,888 --> 00:03:42,889
Your Royal Highness.

31
00:03:51,815 --> 00:03:53,233
How's your father doing?

32
00:03:59,573 --> 00:04:02,909
What's this? A gift?

33
00:04:07,622 --> 00:04:09,332
Your Royal Highness.

34
00:04:11,251 --> 00:04:12,335
Yes?

35
00:04:23,472 --> 00:04:24,639
Let's get a divorce.

36
00:04:48,538 --> 00:04:49,623
What are you talking about?

37
00:04:50,665 --> 00:04:51,666
I think it's time…

38
00:04:56,505 --> 00:04:57,589
we go our separate ways.

39
00:05:17,442 --> 00:05:19,110
Father has fallen ill from all the stress.

40
00:05:21,196 --> 00:05:24,157
The stocks are tanking,
and public sentiment is in the mud.

41
00:05:28,829 --> 00:05:30,580
I heard there's a tax audit coming soon.

42
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:33,124
No wonder he's fallen ill.

43
00:05:38,421 --> 00:05:40,632
I got married to become the successor.

44
00:05:42,384 --> 00:05:43,385
But at this rate,

45
00:05:45,011 --> 00:05:46,847
I won't even have a place to go back to.

46
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,729
I hear what you're saying, but…

47
00:05:54,813 --> 00:05:55,856
It's not your fault.

48
00:05:57,899 --> 00:05:59,359
We were both in the wrong.

49
00:06:07,325 --> 00:06:08,326
But now,

50
00:06:10,412 --> 00:06:11,997
I want to cut my losses.

51
00:06:19,045 --> 00:06:20,255
That's why you want a divorce?

52
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:22,924
To cut your losses?

53
00:06:23,008 --> 00:06:26,386
The quickest fix for stuff like this
is someone stepping up to take the fall.

54
00:06:28,263 --> 00:06:29,931
Holding out isn't always the answer.

55
00:06:36,229 --> 00:06:37,772
Did something happen while I was gone?

56
00:06:38,565 --> 00:06:39,566
Did the Queen Mother--

57
00:06:39,649 --> 00:06:43,028
Whatever the Queen Mother says to me
is none of your concern.

58
00:06:45,113 --> 00:06:46,823
-Seong Huiju.
-I already told you.

59
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:50,535
I'm not afraid of that
because I had no honor to begin with.

60
00:06:52,078 --> 00:06:53,955
Royal dignity, propriety, or whatever.

61
00:06:55,206 --> 00:06:57,083
I couldn't care less
about any of that crap.

62
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:00,712
Does it even exist?

63
00:07:01,838 --> 00:07:03,798
-Seong Huiju!
-Everything I have

64
00:07:05,508 --> 00:07:07,093
actually has substance.

65
00:07:08,136 --> 00:07:10,096
They're things I've fought for…

66
00:07:11,306 --> 00:07:13,016
and claimed with my own hands.

67
00:07:19,773 --> 00:07:21,733
You said the duty
of a royal is to be loved.

68
00:07:23,068 --> 00:07:24,361
You said that was power.

69
00:07:27,656 --> 00:07:29,074
But you lost it all.

70
00:07:31,785 --> 00:07:33,453
What could you possibly do for me now?

71
00:07:46,299 --> 00:07:47,300
Don't do this.

72
00:07:57,185 --> 00:07:59,187
Not you too…

73
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,772
You said you wouldn't hold me back.

74
00:08:03,733 --> 00:08:05,402
You told me to just keep taking.

75
00:08:08,405 --> 00:08:10,198
But I'm just losing everything right now.

76
00:08:13,368 --> 00:08:14,369
And yet…

77
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:18,289
you wish to keep me bound to you?

78
00:09:22,103 --> 00:09:23,104
Your Royal Highness.

79
00:09:23,188 --> 00:09:25,940
This is the Crown Prince's Quarters.

80
00:09:28,818 --> 00:09:30,320
It is a hall without a master.

81
00:09:31,154 --> 00:09:32,155
Your Royal Highness.

82
00:09:32,238 --> 00:09:33,531
I wish to be alone.

83
00:09:35,158 --> 00:09:36,576
Go back to Anhwadang Hall.

84
00:11:47,457 --> 00:11:48,458
Brother.

85
00:11:50,043 --> 00:11:51,502
Look after the Crown Princess.

86
00:11:54,255 --> 00:11:55,840
You are all she has to rely on.

87
00:11:56,966 --> 00:11:58,509
Must you make things hard for her?

88
00:12:01,179 --> 00:12:02,722
She relies on me?

89
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,852
Brother.

90
00:12:07,936 --> 00:12:11,147
I doubt she ever relied on me.

91
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,441
But even if she did,

92
00:12:14,776 --> 00:12:17,153
what could I possibly do for her?

93
00:12:22,742 --> 00:12:24,327
I am sure she is well aware.

94
00:12:26,621 --> 00:12:27,830
Such is the nature

95
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,250
of my station.

96
00:12:32,377 --> 00:12:35,046
And the same must be said
for the Crown Princess.

97
00:12:40,969 --> 00:12:42,720
You are just being a coward.

98
00:12:49,560 --> 00:12:50,561
Sure.

99
00:12:54,274 --> 00:12:55,650
I hope you do not end up like me.

100
00:12:59,946 --> 00:13:00,947
No.

101
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:02,991
I don't intend to.

102
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:19,173
Is this how it felt?

103
00:14:12,852 --> 00:14:14,353
Did you work through the night?

104
00:14:23,321 --> 00:14:24,322
Yeah.

105
00:14:34,332 --> 00:14:35,333
What is it?

106
00:14:36,042 --> 00:14:37,043
What?

107
00:14:37,627 --> 00:14:38,878
Say what you need to say.

108
00:14:45,051 --> 00:14:46,928
Please let me get into the Council Hall.

109
00:14:50,014 --> 00:14:51,808
We need their approval for a divorce.

110
00:14:53,684 --> 00:14:55,019
I'd like to speak for myself.

111
00:15:03,319 --> 00:15:04,320
Do so, then.

112
00:15:14,372 --> 00:15:15,373
Aide Choi.

113
00:15:16,874 --> 00:15:18,501
Are they really going to get divorced?

114
00:15:19,502 --> 00:15:21,546
Well, what can we do?

115
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:23,464
The party involved is intent on it.

116
00:15:23,548 --> 00:15:25,633
And the Grand Prince doesn't get a say?

117
00:15:26,217 --> 00:15:29,554
Well, His Royal Highness agreed to it…

118
00:15:29,637 --> 00:15:32,431
No, but you know he doesn't mean it!

119
00:15:32,515 --> 00:15:34,225
What sort of nonsense is that?

120
00:15:37,436 --> 00:15:38,646
Something happened yesterday.

121
00:15:41,816 --> 00:15:42,984
Is the chairman making her?

122
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:49,490
Your Royal Highness.
By chance, did the chairman--

123
00:15:49,574 --> 00:15:50,575
I'm getting a divorce.

124
00:15:51,242 --> 00:15:52,243
Pardon?

125
00:15:52,326 --> 00:15:53,452
The whole world

126
00:15:54,745 --> 00:15:56,914
refers to me as a stain on his reputation.

127
00:15:58,374 --> 00:16:01,043
-Your Royal Highness, that's just--
-Stain or weakness…

128
00:16:02,712 --> 00:16:04,755
They should be eliminated regardless.

129
00:16:09,635 --> 00:16:11,304
If His Royal Highness refuses…

130
00:16:15,808 --> 00:16:17,018
I need you to take my side.

131
00:16:20,354 --> 00:16:22,148
The chairman is just a bit frustrated.

132
00:16:22,231 --> 00:16:25,318
He didn't put her up to anything.

133
00:16:25,401 --> 00:16:27,778
Then why? Why, all of a sudden?

134
00:16:32,491 --> 00:16:33,826
Don't go anywhere. Wait here.

135
00:16:37,163 --> 00:16:38,497
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

136
00:16:48,966 --> 00:16:50,426
I understand, Your Royal Highness.

137
00:17:03,814 --> 00:17:05,316
Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

138
00:17:17,995 --> 00:17:19,705
LORD INPYEONG

139
00:17:19,789 --> 00:17:20,790
Two days ago,

140
00:17:22,083 --> 00:17:23,167
the Cabinet requested

141
00:17:23,251 --> 00:17:26,712
that His Royal Highness
cease his official duties…

142
00:17:30,967 --> 00:17:32,260
His Royal Highness and I…

143
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:35,763
will be getting a divorce.

144
00:17:38,057 --> 00:17:39,934
-What is this now?
-All of a sudden?

145
00:17:40,017 --> 00:17:41,018
Grand Princess!

146
00:17:42,353 --> 00:17:43,646
Strip me of my rank.

147
00:17:45,523 --> 00:17:47,900
I risked it all to gain royal status,

148
00:17:47,984 --> 00:17:50,152
was a prime suspect
in the Junghwajeon Hall fire,

149
00:17:50,861 --> 00:17:52,822
and collapsed after being poisoned.

150
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:55,866
That was all me.

151
00:17:56,367 --> 00:17:57,368
Grand Princess.

152
00:17:57,451 --> 00:17:59,662
My point is, do not pin this
on the wrong person.

153
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:05,001
It appears you do not grasp
the gravity of this situation.

154
00:18:05,084 --> 00:18:06,085
Prime Minister Min.

155
00:18:08,838 --> 00:18:11,549
I was told the royal family
are not subject to investigation.

156
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:15,344
Without the king's approval,
it is difficult, but…

157
00:18:15,428 --> 00:18:16,721
If I am stripped of my rank,

158
00:18:17,513 --> 00:18:19,348
it should be easier to investigate me, no?

159
00:18:24,103 --> 00:18:26,314
Approve our divorce

160
00:18:28,107 --> 00:18:29,483
and investigate me.

161
00:18:31,986 --> 00:18:32,987
Seong Huiju.

162
00:18:33,696 --> 00:18:36,198
Whether I'm the culprit behind the fire,

163
00:18:36,282 --> 00:18:39,035
or I staged my own collapse.

164
00:18:39,118 --> 00:18:43,122
Either way, I can prove that
the Grand Prince had no part in any of it.

165
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:46,709
So just do it.

166
00:18:47,627 --> 00:18:50,630
And all this insolent talk of him
relinquishing the regency…

167
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:53,466
Enough of that.

168
00:19:09,023 --> 00:19:10,274
Why are there so many?

169
00:19:10,858 --> 00:19:12,401
Babe, you got this, right?

170
00:19:12,902 --> 00:19:14,612
A walk in the park.

171
00:19:15,613 --> 00:19:17,114
Why couldn't she just do it herself?

172
00:19:17,198 --> 00:19:19,283
Huiju is the Grand Princess now.
How could she?

173
00:19:19,367 --> 00:19:21,327
Besides, the camera loves you more.

174
00:19:22,495 --> 00:19:24,121
That's true.

175
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:25,831
Let's go.

176
00:19:29,168 --> 00:19:30,378
There's CEO Seong Taeju!

177
00:19:31,629 --> 00:19:33,089
-CEO Seong!
-CEO Seong!

178
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:35,966
-Please look over here.
-CEO Seong!

179
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:38,886
-CEO Seong!
-Over here, sir!

180
00:19:38,969 --> 00:19:41,013
-Over here, please!
-CEO Seong!

181
00:19:41,097 --> 00:19:44,642
ADDRESSING THE MARRIAGE CONTRACT LEAK

182
00:19:49,730 --> 00:19:50,731
Oh, right.

183
00:19:55,444 --> 00:19:57,863
Can you confirm that Castle Group
had no knowledge

184
00:19:57,947 --> 00:20:00,616
of the marriage contract
between the Grand Prince and Princess?

185
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:04,078
There must be some sort of plan
behind the three-year-divorce promise…

186
00:20:04,161 --> 00:20:06,539
Following the marriage, has the handover
of her management rights

187
00:20:06,622 --> 00:20:08,708
-been properly finalized?
-Just a moment.

188
00:20:08,791 --> 00:20:10,835
First, let's calm down.

189
00:20:10,918 --> 00:20:14,046
There are allegations that she staged
her collapse. Is that true?

190
00:20:15,673 --> 00:20:17,466
-What?
-To hide the fact it was staged,

191
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:20,219
she was taken to Castle Hospital
and not Royal Seoul Hospital.

192
00:20:20,302 --> 00:20:22,263
Is that true?

193
00:20:23,806 --> 00:20:25,850
They're even calling that a lie now?

194
00:20:34,817 --> 00:20:35,818
Ma'am.

195
00:20:36,861 --> 00:20:39,405
Why would she take poison
when she had the world at her feet?

196
00:20:48,289 --> 00:20:49,790
We just got started here.

197
00:20:49,874 --> 00:20:51,834
AIDE CHOI HYEON

198
00:20:56,797 --> 00:20:58,549
Regarding the contract,

199
00:20:58,632 --> 00:21:01,886
Castle Group will be
watering things down on our end.

200
00:21:01,969 --> 00:21:03,721
So I'd appreciate your patience.

201
00:21:03,804 --> 00:21:06,390
It won't be a perfectly clean slate,

202
00:21:06,974 --> 00:21:09,018
but it'll lose enough steam
to make it manageable.

203
00:21:09,101 --> 00:21:11,729
Do you truly believe
it is that simple a matter?

204
00:21:11,812 --> 00:21:14,064
I'm sure you all know how much money

205
00:21:15,566 --> 00:21:16,734
was poured into our wedding.

206
00:21:17,651 --> 00:21:20,863
And that more was made
than was ever spent.

207
00:21:23,157 --> 00:21:24,533
It's surely not news to you.

208
00:21:26,285 --> 00:21:28,788
Before all contributors start asking
for their money back,

209
00:21:29,663 --> 00:21:32,374
shouldn't we at least deny the fact
that this marriage

210
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:34,627
was a sham?

211
00:21:35,878 --> 00:21:36,962
For starters,

212
00:21:37,046 --> 00:21:40,216
I assume all of you have seen
this marriage contract.

213
00:21:41,008 --> 00:21:43,719
Does the Grand Prince benefit
at all from this contract?

214
00:21:43,803 --> 00:21:45,095
Same goes for my sister.

215
00:21:45,179 --> 00:21:47,932
It stipulates that she'll relinquish
all assets and real estate

216
00:21:48,015 --> 00:21:50,351
acquired with her royal title
upon divorce.

217
00:21:50,434 --> 00:21:51,811
Did you all miss that part?

218
00:21:51,894 --> 00:21:54,730
-But this was for status--
-Hold on. Let me just say one thing.

219
00:21:55,397 --> 00:21:58,150
Everyone here knows
the palace was dead set against them

220
00:21:58,234 --> 00:22:01,570
when the scandal
about them dating first broke.

221
00:22:01,654 --> 00:22:04,657
Even our family didn't believe
they would actually get married.

222
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:08,035
We told her to stop wasting time
and just focus on her work.

223
00:22:08,118 --> 00:22:09,411
But what could we do?

224
00:22:09,495 --> 00:22:10,871
They were madly in love.

225
00:22:13,290 --> 00:22:15,417
Well, if they're so madly in love,

226
00:22:15,501 --> 00:22:17,711
why would they agree
to divorce within three years?

227
00:22:18,254 --> 00:22:19,255
Right.

228
00:22:20,047 --> 00:22:22,758
That is why I'm here today.

229
00:22:24,009 --> 00:22:25,386
That clause.

230
00:22:27,096 --> 00:22:29,056
It was per my request.

231
00:22:29,139 --> 00:22:31,934
Does that mean you were
involved in drawing up the contract?

232
00:22:32,017 --> 00:22:33,644
Between the Crown and Castle Group?

233
00:22:33,727 --> 00:22:36,981
They may be madly in love now,
but feelings fade.

234
00:22:37,064 --> 00:22:39,567
I mean, she was even drugged
at her own wedding.

235
00:22:39,650 --> 00:22:41,569
It could make her want a divorce.

236
00:22:41,652 --> 00:22:45,322
But since divorce is considered taboo
in the royal family,

237
00:22:45,406 --> 00:22:48,492
I suggested they at least
draw up a contract.

238
00:22:49,243 --> 00:22:50,578
But let's be real.

239
00:22:50,661 --> 00:22:53,038
This wasn't even notarized by a lawyer.

240
00:22:53,122 --> 00:22:55,916
I just went a little overboard
to protect my little sister.

241
00:22:56,959 --> 00:23:00,254
I sincerely apologize
for the distress caused to the public.

242
00:23:00,337 --> 00:23:01,547
That said…

243
00:23:03,215 --> 00:23:06,677
you all keep spinning these stories
about pulling stunts and plotting treason.

244
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,345
All sorts of ridiculous nonsense…

245
00:23:10,139 --> 00:23:12,308
I'll be saving all your articles as PDFs.

246
00:23:23,068 --> 00:23:24,612
You were so awesome, babe!

247
00:23:25,821 --> 00:23:27,323
-Let's hurry home.
-Okay.

248
00:23:29,074 --> 00:23:30,868
…all your articles as PDFs.

249
00:23:30,951 --> 00:23:33,162
-You reviewed the draft for the PR team?
-Yes.

250
00:23:33,662 --> 00:23:37,041
"Doting siblings," check.
"True love," check.

251
00:23:37,124 --> 00:23:38,709
"Saving as PDFs," check.

252
00:23:39,460 --> 00:23:40,544
All done.

253
00:23:40,628 --> 00:23:41,921
Yes, I knew it!

254
00:23:42,004 --> 00:23:44,924
They couldn't even look at each other
during the wedding rites

255
00:23:45,007 --> 00:23:47,009
without blushing and getting all giddy.

256
00:23:47,092 --> 00:23:50,846
How could that not be true love?

257
00:24:00,439 --> 00:24:01,815
It should be over by now.

258
00:24:01,899 --> 00:24:04,652
Without even consulting
with the Royal Secretariat?

259
00:24:04,735 --> 00:24:08,697
We made it crystal clear that the Crown
has no ties to the contract.

260
00:24:09,281 --> 00:24:13,702
We also clarified that the Grand Prince
stood to gain nothing from our marriage.

261
00:24:14,286 --> 00:24:15,996
Any remaining controversy

262
00:24:16,664 --> 00:24:18,082
will be mine to handle.

263
00:24:19,833 --> 00:24:21,335
Once you cast me aside,

264
00:24:22,670 --> 00:24:24,296
the Grand Prince can return…

265
00:24:26,715 --> 00:24:28,384
to being the pride of the Crown.

266
00:24:34,264 --> 00:24:35,516
Does His Royal Highness…

267
00:24:36,642 --> 00:24:38,352
share this sentiment?

268
00:25:15,305 --> 00:25:16,849
Grand Prince I-AN

269
00:25:16,932 --> 00:25:18,851
shall receive His Majesty's command.

270
00:25:56,764 --> 00:25:58,098
Is this how it felt?

271
00:26:22,164 --> 00:26:23,165
Even so…

272
00:26:29,463 --> 00:26:31,173
I refuse to live like you.

273
00:27:11,380 --> 00:27:12,631
Your Royal Highness.

274
00:27:12,714 --> 00:27:15,384
His Majesty has just retired
to his bedchamber.

275
00:27:15,467 --> 00:27:16,927
-Perhaps you can--
-Announce me.

276
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,388
Your Royal Highness.

277
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:22,516
I told you to announce me.

278
00:27:25,811 --> 00:27:26,979
Your Majesty,

279
00:27:27,062 --> 00:27:28,981
His Royal Highness has arrived.

280
00:27:31,108 --> 00:27:32,317
Show him in.

281
00:27:54,298 --> 00:27:55,299
Your Majesty.

282
00:27:58,427 --> 00:27:59,553
I must ask you

283
00:28:01,305 --> 00:28:02,890
to return my throne.

284
00:28:09,396 --> 00:28:12,149
"Thus proclaims the King."

285
00:28:13,525 --> 00:28:15,152
-"I, the King…"
-I, the King,

286
00:28:15,235 --> 00:28:17,279
being overburdened in body and spirit,

287
00:28:17,362 --> 00:28:19,656
can no longer govern the realm.

288
00:28:21,575 --> 00:28:23,452
Thus, I intend to step down
from the throne.

289
00:28:25,913 --> 00:28:29,041
The Crown Prince is far too young

290
00:28:29,124 --> 00:28:30,792
and of a frail disposition

291
00:28:31,418 --> 00:28:33,086
to assume such a heavy responsibility.

292
00:28:34,129 --> 00:28:36,798
Fortunately, the heavens
have not forsaken us,

293
00:28:37,507 --> 00:28:39,051
and have bestowed upon us the wise

294
00:28:39,718 --> 00:28:41,136
and virtuous Grand Prince I-AN.

295
00:28:41,762 --> 00:28:42,846
"I deem him fit

296
00:28:43,347 --> 00:28:46,558
to serve the heavens
and the royal ancestors above,

297
00:28:46,642 --> 00:28:50,145
and to care for the people
of the realm below."

298
00:28:50,854 --> 00:28:52,648
As such, I, the King,

299
00:28:52,731 --> 00:28:55,067
intend to abdicate the throne
in favor of my uncle,

300
00:28:55,150 --> 00:28:56,944
Grand Prince I-AN.

301
00:28:58,528 --> 00:29:01,323
"All officials of the Crown
and the Cabinet

302
00:29:01,406 --> 00:29:04,368
shall receive and uphold
the new King with might."

303
00:29:06,328 --> 00:29:09,498
And all the people shall
embrace the grand vision of the nation…

304
00:29:09,581 --> 00:29:10,749
"THIRTY-SECOND KING"

305
00:29:10,832 --> 00:29:12,501
…so that the realm may stand firm,

306
00:29:13,293 --> 00:29:16,088
unshaken and everlasting.

307
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,971
What is the meaning of this?

308
00:29:24,805 --> 00:29:26,431
A willful abdication?

309
00:29:26,515 --> 00:29:28,141
I must see His Majesty.

310
00:29:29,601 --> 00:29:30,602
Lord INPYEONG.

311
00:29:31,603 --> 00:29:33,063
Do you dismiss the royal command

312
00:29:35,649 --> 00:29:36,900
delivered by the Royal Secretariat?

313
00:30:01,133 --> 00:30:02,259
Your Royal Highness.

314
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:05,095
Just hold on a second.

315
00:30:17,441 --> 00:30:18,900
You said you were done losing.

316
00:30:21,778 --> 00:30:23,113
That's why you want a divorce.

317
00:30:25,991 --> 00:30:26,992
Your Royal Highness.

318
00:30:27,617 --> 00:30:29,244
-I just…
-And yet,

319
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,747
how could you throw
everything on the line?

320
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:36,293
Did you truly believe…

321
00:30:40,672 --> 00:30:41,673
I could not…

322
00:30:45,802 --> 00:30:46,845
protect us?

323
00:30:51,641 --> 00:30:52,642
It's not that…

324
00:30:52,726 --> 00:30:54,061
You did not trust me.

325
00:31:16,833 --> 00:31:18,168
Willful abdication?

326
00:31:18,251 --> 00:31:22,798
The royal edict was announced in front
of the Cabinet and the royal family.

327
00:31:24,633 --> 00:31:25,801
Why, all of a sudden?

328
00:31:28,345 --> 00:31:29,763
Without so much as a warning.

329
00:31:33,517 --> 00:31:35,685
-Tell me why!
-Please calm down, Your Majesty.

330
00:31:38,063 --> 00:31:40,816
Fortunately, His Royal Highness refused…

331
00:31:40,899 --> 00:31:42,734
That was just a formality!

332
00:31:43,944 --> 00:31:45,612
He will refuse three times…

333
00:31:47,864 --> 00:31:48,949
before he accepts.

334
00:32:02,379 --> 00:32:04,756
That feeble bloodline has at last…

335
00:32:21,189 --> 00:32:22,190
Your Majesty.

336
00:32:22,274 --> 00:32:23,567
Open the doors.

337
00:32:23,650 --> 00:32:26,862
His Majesty has locked them
from the inside.

338
00:32:26,945 --> 00:32:27,946
Your Majesty!

339
00:32:29,698 --> 00:32:31,116
Open these doors!

340
00:32:31,992 --> 00:32:34,411
-Your Majesty!
-Please stop, Your Majesty.

341
00:32:34,494 --> 00:32:36,413
This is beyond the pale.

342
00:32:36,913 --> 00:32:37,914
Your Majesty!

343
00:32:39,875 --> 00:32:42,544
Have you truly gone mad?

344
00:32:44,087 --> 00:32:45,463
I would rather see you dead.

345
00:32:49,301 --> 00:32:50,302
Your Majesty!

346
00:32:50,969 --> 00:32:53,346
Your Majesty,
please give His Majesty some time.

347
00:32:53,430 --> 00:32:55,098
What is this time you speak of?

348
00:32:56,099 --> 00:32:57,100
Your Majesty.

349
00:33:00,103 --> 00:33:01,771
You must have known.

350
00:33:03,064 --> 00:33:04,649
-Pardon?
-Court Lady Im.

351
00:33:04,733 --> 00:33:05,817
Yes, Your Majesty.

352
00:33:07,861 --> 00:33:09,112
Break down these doors.

353
00:33:09,738 --> 00:33:10,739
Your Majesty…

354
00:33:10,822 --> 00:33:12,282
These are the King's Quarters.

355
00:33:12,991 --> 00:33:15,285
How could I open them
without His Majesty's command?

356
00:33:18,288 --> 00:33:20,457
Please rescind your command.

357
00:33:22,834 --> 00:33:24,836
Start a fire if you must.

358
00:33:27,255 --> 00:33:28,798
That should force him out.

359
00:33:37,474 --> 00:33:38,475
Your Majesty.

360
00:33:42,729 --> 00:33:44,272
Let me escort you to your quarters.

361
00:33:45,815 --> 00:33:47,317
Do not give me orders.

362
00:33:49,444 --> 00:33:50,445
I have yet…

363
00:33:52,155 --> 00:33:53,240
to give an order.

364
00:34:07,545 --> 00:34:09,422
We must allow no word of this to spread.

365
00:34:10,590 --> 00:34:12,384
I will handle the Cabinet members.

366
00:34:12,467 --> 00:34:14,886
You must see to it
that no word escapes the palace.

367
00:34:18,890 --> 00:34:21,142
Am I the only one
horrified by this situation?

368
00:34:22,185 --> 00:34:23,478
It is getting quite exhausting.

369
00:34:23,979 --> 00:34:26,940
How much longer must I keep cleaning up
the royal family's mess?

370
00:34:31,569 --> 00:34:33,196
This affects you as well.

371
00:34:37,325 --> 00:34:38,827
If Grand Prince I-AN becomes king,

372
00:34:38,910 --> 00:34:41,079
the Grand Princess will be bound
to the palace forever.

373
00:34:41,162 --> 00:34:42,247
Is that what you desire?

374
00:34:44,332 --> 00:34:45,625
That will not happen.

375
00:34:51,256 --> 00:34:53,675
The Grand Prince will refuse three times
as a formality.

376
00:34:53,758 --> 00:34:57,345
He refused once at the Council Hall today,
so he'll refuse two more times.

377
00:34:57,429 --> 00:34:58,430
Before he does,

378
00:34:59,723 --> 00:35:02,350
you must stop either
the Grand Prince or His Majesty.

379
00:35:04,728 --> 00:35:06,271
Do whatever you must.

380
00:35:12,736 --> 00:35:14,654
I shall put her poisoning case on hold.

381
00:35:15,405 --> 00:35:16,740
But you agreed to handle that--

382
00:35:16,823 --> 00:35:18,700
The handling of affairs you desire

383
00:35:18,783 --> 00:35:20,660
shall be granted to you

384
00:35:22,287 --> 00:35:23,413
once I get what I want.

385
00:35:28,918 --> 00:35:31,421
Are you threatening me right now?

386
00:35:32,213 --> 00:35:33,214
Yes.

387
00:35:34,799 --> 00:35:36,509
Is there any reason I should not?

388
00:35:58,782 --> 00:36:00,241
You did not trust me.

389
00:36:13,922 --> 00:36:16,132
Why is it just you?
Where's the Grand Prince?

390
00:36:16,716 --> 00:36:17,801
He left.

391
00:36:17,884 --> 00:36:20,387
-He left? The palace?
-Yes.

392
00:36:21,429 --> 00:36:24,140
What is he thinking,
leaving at a time like this?

393
00:36:24,933 --> 00:36:26,726
He nearly died as just the Grand Prince.

394
00:36:26,810 --> 00:36:29,521
Who knows what'll happen
after this royal abdication edict?

395
00:36:41,783 --> 00:36:43,034
INCOMING CALL
JUNIOR ALUM

396
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:57,841
Stop it.

397
00:37:01,052 --> 00:37:02,762
How will you ever divorce him
at this rate?

398
00:37:10,019 --> 00:37:12,230
Aide Choi and I will find
the Grand Prince.

399
00:37:13,022 --> 00:37:14,315
You stay here.

400
00:37:14,399 --> 00:37:15,942
Can't have you missing each other.

401
00:37:53,104 --> 00:37:54,898
If I say I wish to ascend the throne,

402
00:37:56,107 --> 00:37:57,859
all would condemn me and hurl insults.

403
00:38:01,696 --> 00:38:02,697
But I believe

404
00:38:03,823 --> 00:38:04,991
you would understand me.

405
00:38:09,871 --> 00:38:10,955
"Leading the way."

406
00:38:11,831 --> 00:38:12,832
How do you do it?

407
00:38:15,877 --> 00:38:17,420
You just need to walk by my side.

408
00:38:19,339 --> 00:38:20,465
I'll teach you.

409
00:38:50,537 --> 00:38:51,871
Just let me be for a second.

410
00:38:52,539 --> 00:38:54,666
I'll come back down
once my anger subsides a bit.

411
00:39:21,609 --> 00:39:22,610
I do like you.

412
00:39:24,237 --> 00:39:25,238
And it's my first time.

413
00:39:26,239 --> 00:39:27,574
You should just accept it all.

414
00:39:29,325 --> 00:39:30,952
Whether it be money, honor,

415
00:39:32,745 --> 00:39:33,746
or my heart…

416
00:40:31,095 --> 00:40:33,014
Aide Do, here's what you asked for.

417
00:40:33,556 --> 00:40:35,433
-Let's go.
-Where?

418
00:40:35,516 --> 00:40:38,978
His Royal Highness left the palace
and won't take the Grand Princess's calls.

419
00:40:39,062 --> 00:40:41,189
What? What about the Royal Guard?

420
00:40:41,272 --> 00:40:43,566
No need to call them. I know where he is.

421
00:40:43,650 --> 00:40:45,610
After the royal abdication edict
is delivered,

422
00:40:45,693 --> 00:40:48,446
His Majesty will lock himself
in his quarters.

423
00:40:49,113 --> 00:40:51,240
I will leave and head to
my private residence.

424
00:40:51,908 --> 00:40:53,284
I must be gone

425
00:40:53,952 --> 00:40:55,995
so the Grand Princess
does not get embroiled in the chaos.

426
00:40:57,705 --> 00:40:59,207
I understand, Your Royal Highness.

427
00:40:59,916 --> 00:41:02,168
Wow, so you knew all along?

428
00:41:02,251 --> 00:41:04,045
Then why didn't you loop me in?

429
00:41:04,963 --> 00:41:06,965
You didn't loop me in, either.

430
00:41:07,048 --> 00:41:08,466
About the Grand Princess's plan.

431
00:41:09,467 --> 00:41:10,677
Right. That's true.

432
00:41:12,345 --> 00:41:13,972
Wait, so where are we going?

433
00:41:14,055 --> 00:41:16,182
-To get a drink.
-What?

434
00:41:24,482 --> 00:41:26,109
Everything's a mess anyway.

435
00:41:26,192 --> 00:41:28,945
Might as well have a drink
since it's not allowed in the palace.

436
00:41:29,028 --> 00:41:30,989
Well, th-that's true…

437
00:41:41,124 --> 00:41:42,125
This is it.

438
00:41:42,834 --> 00:41:44,168
This is what I like.

439
00:41:46,629 --> 00:41:47,630
That's random.

440
00:41:51,467 --> 00:41:52,719
You asked what I liked.

441
00:41:54,262 --> 00:41:55,304
This is what I like.

442
00:41:56,472 --> 00:41:57,515
With the Hangang River here.

443
00:42:20,913 --> 00:42:22,123
What do you think?

444
00:42:23,291 --> 00:42:24,292
Well, it's…

445
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:27,003
I-I like it.

446
00:42:32,467 --> 00:42:33,593
What exactly?

447
00:42:34,886 --> 00:42:35,928
The river?

448
00:42:37,346 --> 00:42:38,347
The alcohol?

449
00:42:40,141 --> 00:42:41,142
Or me?

450
00:43:29,982 --> 00:43:32,902
I like it all. I like the whole lot.

451
00:43:38,282 --> 00:43:39,450
Where are you?

452
00:43:40,034 --> 00:43:41,577
Did you have dinner?

453
00:43:41,661 --> 00:43:45,164
I get that you're angry and all,
but how could you just leave like this?

454
00:43:46,165 --> 00:43:48,334
You're somewhere safe, right?

455
00:43:48,417 --> 00:43:50,503
I swear, I will track your location.

456
00:43:52,130 --> 00:43:55,216
Is Aide Do even looking for him or what?

457
00:43:57,593 --> 00:43:58,594
Your Royal Highness.

458
00:44:00,179 --> 00:44:01,180
Yes?

459
00:44:04,475 --> 00:44:07,645
There was this one day
when His Royal Highness

460
00:44:09,063 --> 00:44:11,190
climbed over this wall.

461
00:44:14,569 --> 00:44:16,696
He seemed exceptionally happy that day.

462
00:44:17,488 --> 00:44:20,074
I wondered if he'd hidden
a sweet pot of honey here.

463
00:44:20,158 --> 00:44:22,076
It wasn't until the next day
that I found out

464
00:44:22,827 --> 00:44:24,370
that a maiden was responsible.

465
00:44:26,956 --> 00:44:28,082
And so,

466
00:44:28,666 --> 00:44:30,251
I have faith in the both of you.

467
00:44:31,252 --> 00:44:34,505
You are both desperate
to protect one another, are you not?

468
00:44:38,968 --> 00:44:40,595
The palace gates will be shut soon.

469
00:44:47,018 --> 00:44:48,144
Then can I just…

470
00:44:50,813 --> 00:44:52,148
Oh.

471
00:44:52,231 --> 00:44:53,816
But what if someone asks for me?

472
00:44:53,900 --> 00:44:55,443
Do not worry.

473
00:45:45,534 --> 00:45:46,702
I'm sick.

474
00:45:46,786 --> 00:45:49,288
PRINCE

475
00:46:33,207 --> 00:46:34,208
I thought you were sick.

476
00:46:36,961 --> 00:46:38,546
I just wanted to be with you.

477
00:46:43,467 --> 00:46:45,052
I told you I'd be back tomorrow.

478
00:46:47,179 --> 00:46:48,180
Are you okay?

479
00:47:02,611 --> 00:47:03,738
I like you.

480
00:47:27,970 --> 00:47:28,971
Stick to one thing.

481
00:47:30,306 --> 00:47:31,432
I'm getting confused.

482
00:47:33,726 --> 00:47:34,977
No, you're not.

483
00:47:37,897 --> 00:47:38,939
You know I like you.

484
00:47:41,275 --> 00:47:43,569
And that I only asked
for a divorce to protect you.

485
00:47:46,447 --> 00:47:47,782
That's why you're mad.

486
00:48:24,026 --> 00:48:25,069
You don't want this?

487
00:48:35,037 --> 00:48:36,038
I do.

488
00:50:20,100 --> 00:50:21,101
Your Royal Highness?

489
00:50:29,693 --> 00:50:30,694
You're awake.

490
00:50:32,196 --> 00:50:33,197
What's going on?

491
00:50:35,824 --> 00:50:37,117
I got a call from the palace.

492
00:50:40,496 --> 00:50:41,497
What's wrong?

493
00:50:43,082 --> 00:50:44,291
Did you have a nightmare?

494
00:50:48,420 --> 00:50:50,297
I was just a little scared.

495
00:50:58,806 --> 00:51:00,349
Stay here for the time being.

496
00:51:02,017 --> 00:51:04,228
By myself? Why?

497
00:51:05,020 --> 00:51:06,730
The second edict will be delivered soon.

498
00:51:08,274 --> 00:51:09,275
And I will

499
00:51:10,192 --> 00:51:11,360
refuse it once more.

500
00:51:12,695 --> 00:51:13,696
Hold on a second.

501
00:51:15,489 --> 00:51:16,657
One step at a time.

502
00:51:16,740 --> 00:51:19,368
Walk me through step by step
so I can understand.

503
00:51:21,161 --> 00:51:22,454
With a royal abdication edict,

504
00:51:23,956 --> 00:51:25,583
it's customary to refuse three times.

505
00:51:27,042 --> 00:51:28,419
And then?

506
00:51:30,337 --> 00:51:31,380
I have to accept it.

507
00:51:34,008 --> 00:51:36,343
But you wanted to protect His Majesty.

508
00:51:41,432 --> 00:51:42,975
I wanted to protect my nephew.

509
00:51:45,311 --> 00:51:46,312
Not the king.

510
00:51:51,609 --> 00:51:53,736
Whoosh.

511
00:51:53,819 --> 00:51:55,404
Whoosh.

512
00:51:55,487 --> 00:51:58,282
You intend for Grand Prince I-AN
to ascend the throne?

513
00:51:59,491 --> 00:52:02,828
Have you truly gone mad?

514
00:52:33,817 --> 00:52:34,860
What is this?

515
00:52:35,778 --> 00:52:40,115
His Majesty had a garment made for you.

516
00:53:04,390 --> 00:53:05,391
It appears my brother…

517
00:53:07,976 --> 00:53:09,436
seeks to abdicate.

518
00:53:09,978 --> 00:53:12,147
But what about the Crown Prince?

519
00:53:14,149 --> 00:53:15,401
I hated him for it.

520
00:53:16,819 --> 00:53:19,113
He turned a blind eye
when I longed for it so desperately.

521
00:53:20,322 --> 00:53:23,951
It felt like he was thrusting the burden
when it was far too late.

522
00:53:24,034 --> 00:53:25,202
Your Royal Highness!

523
00:53:31,417 --> 00:53:33,043
Something terrible has happened.

524
00:53:35,629 --> 00:53:36,630
But…

525
00:53:41,677 --> 00:53:42,845
I was the one too late.

526
00:53:55,941 --> 00:53:59,278
So I wanted to protect my nephew,
no matter what.

527
00:54:00,738 --> 00:54:01,780
In my brother's place.

528
00:54:03,490 --> 00:54:05,033
Where is the Crown Prince?

529
00:54:05,576 --> 00:54:06,577
Pardon?

530
00:54:06,660 --> 00:54:08,287
Where is my nephew…

531
00:54:10,372 --> 00:54:11,749
the heir to the throne?

532
00:54:17,504 --> 00:54:18,505
When the Queen Mother

533
00:54:20,257 --> 00:54:22,176
turned a blind eye
to my brother's dying wish…

534
00:54:29,433 --> 00:54:31,185
Even when my nephew told me he was scared…

535
00:54:37,983 --> 00:54:39,067
I hesitated.

536
00:54:49,453 --> 00:54:50,537
If I become king,

537
00:54:52,039 --> 00:54:53,707
I feel like I could protect everyone.

538
00:54:56,793 --> 00:54:57,794
But then again…

539
00:55:02,633 --> 00:55:04,009
I fear it's just my own greed.

540
00:55:16,063 --> 00:55:17,147
You can be greedy.

541
00:55:23,946 --> 00:55:24,947
Let's see this through.

542
00:55:27,824 --> 00:55:28,992
I will be by your side.

543
00:55:46,760 --> 00:55:49,680
Remove Grand Prince I-AN as regent!

544
00:55:49,763 --> 00:55:51,807
-Remove him!
-Remove him!

545
00:55:51,890 --> 00:55:54,851
Strip Seong Huiju of her rank immediately!

546
00:55:54,935 --> 00:55:56,937
-Immediately!
-Immediately!

547
00:55:57,020 --> 00:56:00,524
Grand Prince I-AN and
CEO Seong Huiju must apologize!

548
00:56:00,607 --> 00:56:02,526
Apologize! Apologize!

549
00:56:02,609 --> 00:56:03,610
Your Royal Highness.

550
00:56:05,279 --> 00:56:06,989
The Queen Mother is asking for you.

551
00:56:16,999 --> 00:56:18,000
All right.

552
00:56:45,736 --> 00:56:47,070
Tell them you cannot accept.

553
00:56:54,953 --> 00:56:56,788
Surely you do not intend to accept.

554
00:56:59,249 --> 00:57:01,918
His Majesty has
only eight years of life to his name.

555
00:57:02,002 --> 00:57:04,212
He is incapable
of forming thoughts or intentions!

556
00:57:04,296 --> 00:57:05,422
That is it!

557
00:57:07,841 --> 00:57:09,468
That is exactly the issue.

558
00:57:11,178 --> 00:57:12,262
He has no will

559
00:57:12,929 --> 00:57:15,557
or mind of his own, yet you have him
sit up there as a puppet

560
00:57:15,641 --> 00:57:17,142
tossing him about as you please!

561
00:57:19,978 --> 00:57:21,396
That is precisely the issue.

562
00:57:23,565 --> 00:57:25,567
Is that what you told His Majesty?

563
00:57:27,319 --> 00:57:30,572
You are the one who made
the king into a puppet!

564
00:57:32,199 --> 00:57:33,200
Yes.

565
00:57:34,618 --> 00:57:35,786
I let that happen.

566
00:57:37,496 --> 00:57:40,082
Whether beside or behind him,
he was easily pushed around.

567
00:57:42,542 --> 00:57:43,585
So now…

568
00:57:45,921 --> 00:57:47,214
I must stand in front of him.

569
00:57:49,633 --> 00:57:51,009
I-AN!

570
00:57:59,267 --> 00:58:00,268
Queen Mother.

571
00:58:02,437 --> 00:58:04,940
You should be thankful
he stepped down on his own.

572
00:58:06,608 --> 00:58:08,360
In consideration of his filial devotion,

573
00:58:09,903 --> 00:58:10,987
I will not ask you…

574
00:58:12,989 --> 00:58:14,116
to pay for your sins.

575
00:58:18,578 --> 00:58:19,579
Why?

576
00:58:22,499 --> 00:58:25,252
Why insist on becoming king only now?

577
00:58:35,887 --> 00:58:37,389
I have made my sacrifices.

578
00:58:39,641 --> 00:58:41,351
So you must do the same.

579
00:58:43,103 --> 00:58:45,188
That is only fair!

580
00:59:02,289 --> 00:59:03,749
I gave up on my dreams.

581
00:59:10,297 --> 00:59:13,008
You must become the Crown Princess.

582
00:59:15,218 --> 00:59:16,553
My future.

583
00:59:21,308 --> 00:59:22,476
Yun Irang!

584
00:59:44,289 --> 00:59:46,333
And even my heart.

585
00:59:48,752 --> 00:59:49,753
So why?

586
00:59:51,963 --> 00:59:54,591
Why won't you give anything up?

587
01:00:22,494 --> 01:00:23,787
Court Lady Im, are you there?

588
01:00:30,418 --> 01:00:32,337
Her Majesty appears weary
in mind and body.

589
01:00:33,713 --> 01:00:34,798
For the next three days,

590
01:00:36,424 --> 01:00:38,176
permit no one to enter her quarters.

591
01:00:38,969 --> 01:00:40,929
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

592
01:00:54,401 --> 01:00:56,278
Your Majesty…

593
01:01:07,747 --> 01:01:10,083
What on earth are you doing?

594
01:01:10,667 --> 01:01:12,460
If His Majesty refused to open the doors,

595
01:01:12,544 --> 01:01:14,754
you should've torn them down!

596
01:01:16,631 --> 01:01:19,050
Never mind.
I will head there now--

597
01:01:19,134 --> 01:01:20,552
It will all be in vain.

598
01:01:21,928 --> 01:01:23,054
For the next three days,

599
01:01:24,764 --> 01:01:27,350
no one will be permitted
to enter my quarters.

600
01:01:27,976 --> 01:01:29,019
And why is that?

601
01:01:30,353 --> 01:01:32,188
If the Grand Prince accepts
the abdication,

602
01:01:32,272 --> 01:01:34,274
he will destroy us.

603
01:01:38,945 --> 01:01:41,323
He has stated
he will not hold me accountable.

604
01:01:41,406 --> 01:01:42,449
Do you really believe…

605
01:01:45,535 --> 01:01:49,247
Ignoring the late King's dying wish
isn't our only crime.

606
01:01:50,123 --> 01:01:52,334
Even if Prime Minister Min
is covering for us now,

607
01:01:52,417 --> 01:01:54,753
-if he becomes king--
-That is enough!

608
01:01:55,253 --> 01:01:58,548
Do you intend to surrender
all privileges held by the royal family?

609
01:01:58,632 --> 01:01:59,799
Father!

610
01:02:01,092 --> 01:02:02,928
I will take over from here.

611
01:02:06,431 --> 01:02:08,099
What are you plotting now?

612
01:02:08,183 --> 01:02:10,518
It will be too late after his ascension.

613
01:02:11,853 --> 01:02:13,480
What does that mean?

614
01:02:13,563 --> 01:02:15,065
Your Majesty,

615
01:02:16,149 --> 01:02:17,901
you just need to protect your quarters.

616
01:02:20,737 --> 01:02:21,738
Father?

617
01:02:37,170 --> 01:02:39,631
Lord INPYEONG, you have a guest.

618
01:03:30,598 --> 01:03:33,727
-Wow. Is this what he's wearing today?
-Yes.

619
01:03:34,227 --> 01:03:37,689
The last edict will be
personally delivered by His Majesty.

620
01:03:37,772 --> 01:03:42,318
But he didn't wear this
to His Majesty's Royal Birthday Banquet?

621
01:03:42,402 --> 01:03:43,820
Thank you for bringing that up.

622
01:03:43,903 --> 01:03:46,114
I went through hell that day--

623
01:03:52,370 --> 01:03:53,371
Oh…

624
01:03:54,831 --> 01:03:56,791
His Majesty, the late King,

625
01:03:57,751 --> 01:03:59,419
would have been delighted to see this.

626
01:04:04,841 --> 01:04:05,925
I'm delighted too.

627
01:04:09,888 --> 01:04:11,056
Your Royal Highness.

628
01:04:14,684 --> 01:04:15,977
The Royal Secretariat has notified

629
01:04:16,061 --> 01:04:18,021
the Office of Royal Relatives
and the Prime Minister.

630
01:04:18,104 --> 01:04:20,940
Goodness, they'll all be racing
to the palace now.

631
01:04:21,024 --> 01:04:22,108
Before that, we have

632
01:04:22,192 --> 01:04:24,694
some documents from the Secretariat
and Rites for your review.

633
01:04:25,445 --> 01:04:26,446
Are you ready to go?

634
01:04:37,499 --> 01:04:38,792
I'll be waiting here.

635
01:04:40,627 --> 01:04:41,628
Okay.

636
01:05:00,855 --> 01:05:02,190
Your Majesty,

637
01:05:02,273 --> 01:05:04,109
His Majesty has arrived.

638
01:05:12,784 --> 01:05:14,119
What brings you here?

639
01:05:15,912 --> 01:05:16,996
Mother.

640
01:05:17,080 --> 01:05:20,125
If you do not intend to rescind it,
you should turn back.

641
01:05:20,208 --> 01:05:21,626
I…

642
01:05:21,709 --> 01:05:23,545
Your father fought to protect that throne!

643
01:05:28,133 --> 01:05:32,637
Do you have any idea
what he went through to safeguard it?

644
01:05:33,179 --> 01:05:36,141
Do you know what I had to do
to ensure it was passed down to you--

645
01:05:36,224 --> 01:05:37,892
I know!

646
01:05:38,935 --> 01:05:42,313
The day Father passed away…

647
01:05:43,940 --> 01:05:46,693
I heard everything.

648
01:06:02,542 --> 01:06:03,751
How…

649
01:06:03,835 --> 01:06:06,087
I do not want to!

650
01:06:09,048 --> 01:06:10,091
Crown Prince!

651
01:06:10,717 --> 01:06:13,720
I do not want to!

652
01:06:16,681 --> 01:06:18,183
It was your father's dying wish.

653
01:06:22,979 --> 01:06:25,982
The only one I can rely on now
is you, Crown Prince…

654
01:06:28,651 --> 01:06:30,278
No. Your Majesty.

655
01:06:33,823 --> 01:06:35,700
Do not disappoint me.

656
01:07:01,851 --> 01:07:03,519
Mother!

657
01:07:10,985 --> 01:07:14,572
Mother, please forgive me

658
01:07:15,406 --> 01:07:16,824
for disappointing you.

659
01:08:03,413 --> 01:08:04,414
Sir.

660
01:08:05,081 --> 01:08:06,916
It's time to head to the Council Hall now.

661
01:08:08,376 --> 01:08:09,919
There's still plenty of time.

662
01:08:12,005 --> 01:08:13,006
Yes, sir.

663
01:08:36,446 --> 01:08:38,781
I will take over from here.

664
01:08:42,035 --> 01:08:44,954
You must stop either
the Grand Prince or His Majesty.

665
01:08:45,038 --> 01:08:46,372
Do whatever you must.

666
01:08:49,375 --> 01:08:50,501
I will not ask you

667
01:08:52,462 --> 01:08:53,588
to pay for your sins.

668
01:09:02,930 --> 01:09:04,432
I-AN

669
01:09:10,605 --> 01:09:12,857
Your Royal Highness,
it is the Queen Mother.

670
01:09:20,239 --> 01:09:22,617
I'd like a brief audience
in the Council Hall.

671
01:09:23,201 --> 01:09:25,453
Do we have time
before we're due at the Throne Hall?

672
01:09:26,037 --> 01:09:26,913
Well…

673
01:09:27,955 --> 01:09:30,375
Yes, we have about 30 minutes.

674
01:09:31,125 --> 01:09:32,126
Right.

675
01:09:48,267 --> 01:09:49,519
Court Lady Im.

676
01:09:55,817 --> 01:09:57,193
Yes, Your Majesty.

677
01:10:00,988 --> 01:10:02,323
I need the girl I hid…

678
01:10:06,619 --> 01:10:08,079
brought to the palace.

679
01:10:11,874 --> 01:10:13,960
PROTOCOL FOR THE ACCESSION
OF THE 34TH KING

680
01:10:16,295 --> 01:10:17,839
Be honest with me.

681
01:10:18,506 --> 01:10:19,549
About what?

682
01:10:20,425 --> 01:10:21,551
If I become…

683
01:10:22,677 --> 01:10:24,470
If I become the Queen,

684
01:10:25,722 --> 01:10:27,515
people wouldn't like it, right?

685
01:10:28,808 --> 01:10:31,144
Come on now. Your Royal Highness?
Who would ever?

686
01:10:31,227 --> 01:10:33,563
My goodness. Who would dare?

687
01:10:33,646 --> 01:10:34,647
If I ever find them…

688
01:10:34,731 --> 01:10:36,983
Hyejeong would've been
brutally honest with me.

689
01:10:38,151 --> 01:10:40,153
Yes. Well, they won't be too thrilled.

690
01:10:42,822 --> 01:10:44,532
Right, exactly!

691
01:10:44,615 --> 01:10:47,285
If I had known about this,
I wouldn't have stepped up.

692
01:10:47,368 --> 01:10:49,120
I was planning
to just take the fall for it

693
01:10:49,203 --> 01:10:51,748
and bounce out of here
without looking back.

694
01:10:51,831 --> 01:10:53,207
No need to get worked up.

695
01:10:53,750 --> 01:10:58,546
Not everyone is a fan
of the Grand Prince, either.

696
01:10:59,630 --> 01:11:01,090
I only have haters.

697
01:11:01,174 --> 01:11:02,884
Oh, I see.

698
01:11:04,802 --> 01:11:05,803
You can do it!

699
01:11:07,889 --> 01:11:10,099
PAIN IN MY ASS

700
01:11:13,978 --> 01:11:14,979
Yes?

701
01:11:15,062 --> 01:11:19,609
Hey, you said you'd call.
I've been waiting forever, you know.

702
01:11:19,692 --> 01:11:22,111
Should I move to the next step?
Father in the hospital?

703
01:11:22,195 --> 01:11:24,655
No. Don't. Just stop that for now.

704
01:11:24,739 --> 01:11:27,617
Stop? Why? Are they
calling off the company audit?

705
01:11:28,826 --> 01:11:30,328
No, that's not it.

706
01:11:31,913 --> 01:11:34,040
Where are you now? Father's place?

707
01:11:34,123 --> 01:11:36,542
-Yeah.
-Stay there. I'll be right over.

708
01:11:36,626 --> 01:11:38,169
At least tell me what's going…

709
01:11:38,252 --> 01:11:39,420
Damn brat.

710
01:11:40,379 --> 01:11:42,173
Why? What did Huiju say?

711
01:11:42,757 --> 01:11:44,675
-She's coming here.
-What?

712
01:12:18,626 --> 01:12:19,627
Grand Princess.

713
01:12:20,253 --> 01:12:21,254
You must flee.

714
01:12:22,588 --> 01:12:25,424
Isn't that… the Council Hall?

715
01:12:45,486 --> 01:12:46,571
No…

716
01:12:47,113 --> 01:12:48,573
No!

717
01:12:49,782 --> 01:12:50,783
Your Highness!

718
01:13:11,512 --> 01:13:12,513
Aide Do.

719
01:13:13,014 --> 01:13:14,015
What…

720
01:13:16,976 --> 01:13:18,185
What are you doing here?

721
01:13:23,900 --> 01:13:24,901
Tell me.

722
01:13:28,237 --> 01:13:29,405
Do Hyejeong!

723
01:13:29,947 --> 01:13:30,948
The Council Hall…

724
01:13:33,951 --> 01:13:35,036
His Royal Highness.

725
01:13:36,078 --> 01:13:37,413
He's in the Council Hall.

726
01:13:51,093 --> 01:13:52,094
Your Royal Highness.

727
01:13:57,808 --> 01:13:58,809
Your Royal Highness.

728
01:14:06,609 --> 01:14:09,528
PERFECT CROWN

729
01:14:46,107 --> 01:14:47,692
His Royal Highness.

730
01:14:47,775 --> 01:14:48,985
He's in the Council Hall.

731
01:14:49,068 --> 01:14:50,486
Your Royal Highness!

732
01:14:50,569 --> 01:14:52,613
Your Royal Highness!

733
01:14:52,697 --> 01:14:55,658
There's a rumor circulating
that the Grand Prince has passed away.

734
01:14:55,741 --> 01:14:56,867
What do you mean, regency?

735
01:14:56,951 --> 01:14:59,286
Since the Grand Prince
remains unconscious,

736
01:14:59,370 --> 01:15:01,956
it would only be fitting
for Your Majesty to step forward.

737
01:15:02,039 --> 01:15:03,416
The Grand Prince is awake!

738
01:15:06,794 --> 01:15:09,463
I hear rumors of my passing
are spreading outside these walls.

739
01:15:09,547 --> 01:15:12,466
How could one measly royal guard
blow up the Council Hall by himself?

740
01:15:12,550 --> 01:15:14,301
Since the Grand Prince
has regained consciousness,

741
01:15:14,385 --> 01:15:16,262
it's time we tied up some loose ends.

742
01:15:16,804 --> 01:15:19,348
How much do you trust Jeongwoo?

743
01:15:20,266 --> 01:15:22,977
Is there any place safe for you?

744
01:15:25,855 --> 01:15:27,815
Translated by Justin S. Kim

745
01:15:39,118 --> 01:15:42,830
PERFECT CROWN
